  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bb0\u0bb7\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd : \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8 - \u0b9c\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bbf \u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka may get fuel from Russia: US has no intention of setting up a military base in Sri Lanka - Julie Sung",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United States has not imposed any restrictions on Sri Lanka receiving aid from Russia. But we have banned fuel imports from Russia to America. We have sufficient reservoir energy capacity. But globally, the banking system and transportation system for Russia is banned. US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sung said that Sri Lanka should understand about it.",
        "You cannot try to solve the economic crisis alone without political restructuring. In the midst of the crisis, there is a great opportunity to bring about restructuring in both sectors. America has been a long time friend of Sri Lanka. We have been providing aid to Sri Lanka for 70 years. Crisis or not, we will continue to be Sri Lanka's best friend. We do not support any individual or party in this. Instead we express our support to the people of Sri Lanka.",
        "The International Monetary Fund is the only option for Sri Lanka in the current environment. Sri Lanka believes so. Everyone, including world economists, is talking about this. All insist that Sri Lanka should seek the International Monetary Fund.",
        "America is helping the people of Sri Lanka. Our assistance and cooperation is not limited to the incumbent president. Not with the Prime Minister. It is with the people of Sri Lanka. It is wrong to say that international countries are waiting to help after the regime change in Sri Lanka. Because standing in queues are ordinary people. And international institutions will not lend readily to a country that has not been restructured. So the International Monetary Fund is the only way out.",
        "The US has not imposed any restrictions on Sri Lanka receiving aid from Russia. But we have banned fuel imports from Russia to America. We have sufficient reservoir energy capacity. But globally, the banking system and transportation system for Russia is banned. Sri Lanka should understand that.",
        "US military base in Sri Lanka MCC A false message was spread that it would be established through an agreement. We have no intention of establishing a US military base in Sri Lanka. But people still ask me that. We have signed MCC agreement globally. Nepal has recently recognized it. Sri Lanka lost that opportunity and now there is no move to bring MC, C. Considerations in this regard may come in the future.",
        "We emphasize the need for economic and political restructuring. Sri Lankan people and government should decide how to do it. Sri Lanka must decide whether it is constitutional reform or a caretaker government."
      ],
